---
title: Quick Indian Coconut Beef Curry & Garlic Rice with Radish Salad & Coriander
description: This easy unforgettable Indian beef curry gets the royal treatment with simmered spices, aromatic garlic rice and a finish of
creamy coconut sauce. Who knew something that takes so little effort could be so tasty?
